Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.23,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它的运行与复制\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the instructions for running and reproducing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:21.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}经由精密的生命机器所操纵\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the intricate machinery of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生命的基本信息\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The essential message of life
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:27.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经被反复复制了3百万年\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has been copied and recopied for more than 3 billion years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:30.44,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但这些信息从何而来？\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But where did that message come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:32.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无人知晓\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Nobody knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:45.56,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许它就诞生于这样一个阳光照射的浅水塘\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Perhaps it began in a shallow, sunlit pool, just like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:48.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知何时起\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Somehow, carbon-rich molecules
