Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.93,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}某些分子变体具有更好的复制能力\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some varieties were better at making copies,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.97,0:07:56.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并留下了更多的后代\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and left more offspring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:59.94,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分子间的竞争让它们变得日益精巧\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The competing molecules became more elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:03.81,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}进化与生命由此悄然而生\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Evolution and life itself was underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.41,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许 生命是源于\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Or life could've started
