Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:13.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深藏于海底\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on the deep sea floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:20.63,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}甚至有没有可能 生命是搭着顺风车自天而降\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Or is it possible that life came to Earth
