Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:24.50,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让我来跟你说个故事\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Let me tell you a story
