Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:35.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在亚历山大附近有一个宁静的埃及小村庄\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The peace of the Egyptian village of Nakhla,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:36.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫纳卡垃\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}near Alexandria,
