Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:56.66,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这块陨石上记载着\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Written in this meteorite was
