Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.07,0:23:40.53,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类已经像这样向太空发送信息\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We've been sending our stories into space
