Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.08,0:23:50.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果这些星球上的文明\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If any of these worlds are home
