Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.90,0:24:49.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个很简单的阶段\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in our technological development.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.57,0:24:52.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当我们设想着外星文明\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When we imagine alien civilizations
