Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.98,0:25:05.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比人类更先进的外星文明\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Civilizations even slightly more advanced than ours
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.92,0:25:07.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许已经发展到\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}may have already moved on
