Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.20,0:25:15.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们的信息很有可能\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Their messages could be
