Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.53,0:25:21.20,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可我们不懂得怎么去捕获它\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but we lack the means to perceive them,
