Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.74,0:25:27.94,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人们经常会察觉不到\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}would have been oblivious to the most urgent radio signal
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.94,0:25:30.81,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从别的地方传来的无线电呼救信号\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.81,0:25:33.98,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有一个更棘手的可能性\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But there's another, more troubling possibility--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.98,0:25:36.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}文明和生命体一样\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}civilizations, like other living things,
