Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.52,0:25:41.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或者是自行造成的毁灭\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}due to natural causes, or violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.79,0:25:44.09,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在生存过一段时间以后便会消亡\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or self-inflicted wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.13,0:25:46.43,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎样 我们已经尽力\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Whether or not we ever make contact
