Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.34,0:26:33.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是哪里出了差错？\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What went wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.78,0:26:36.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其中一个重要的原因就是发生在美索不达亚平原的城邦之间的那些\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}One problem was the almost ceaseless warfare
