Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.42,0:26:41.05,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}摧毁了人类的成就\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which continually destroyed their achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.09,0:26:43.22,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伟大的军功\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They glorified military conquest
