Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.09,0:26:51.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}另一个消亡的原因\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Another cause of decline
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.16,0:26:52.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是他们的技术知识\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}was that their technical know-how
