Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.33,0:26:58.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}巧妙的灌溉系统\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ingenious irrigation system that was the basis
