Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.19,0:29:32.09,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它喷出的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It spewed hundreds of times more
