Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.67,0:30:56.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这说明做这些工具的人\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This tells us that some toolmakers,
