Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.44,0:31:26.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}具有威胁性的那些能量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}before it explodes.
