Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.45,0:36:53.56,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还要多出数百倍\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than the present age of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.59,0:36:55.39,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果智能生命可以永恒存在\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What would intelligent beings do
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.43,0:36:56.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们会做些什么\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if they had an eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.93,0:37:00.23,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来拓展他们对于宇宙的了解？\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to develop their understanding of the universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.26,0:37:02.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许他们能找到在宇宙开启\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Perhaps they would learn how to open shortcuts
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.50,0:37:04.63,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}时空隧道的方法\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the fabric of spacetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.67,0:37:06.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从而在不同的星系之间\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to travel between galaxies
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.60,0:37:08.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以比光速更快的速度旅行\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}faster than the speed of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.44,0:37:11.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许他们能创造出全新的宇宙\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe they would create whole new universes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.31,0:37:14.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像是艺术或科学的实验\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as artistic or scientific experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.81,0:37:17.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可现在 至少是在地球上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Of course no one, or at least nobody on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.68,0:37:20.45,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没人知道永生的人会做什么\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}knows what the immortals might do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.68,0:37:25.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要发挥一下无限的想象力\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If one allows the imagination free reign.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.79,0:37:27.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可我们呢？\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But what about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.49,0:37:32.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的未来会是怎样？\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What is our own future?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.86,0:37:34.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙的年历\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What would the Cosmic Calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.90,0:37:38.63,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在下一个140亿年里会是什么样子？\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the next 14 billion years look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.35,0:37:54.19,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果最初的宇宙年历\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If the original Cosmic Calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.22,0:37:56.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}包含了宇宙诞生至今的所有时间\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}includes all of time from the birth of the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.72,0:37:58.66,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到现在这一刻\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}until this very moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.69,0:38:01.56,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么宇宙的年历\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what would the Cosmic Calendar look like
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.59,0:38:05.36,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在下一个140亿年里会是什么样子？\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for the next 14 billion years?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.40,0:38:07.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和过去的宇宙年历一致\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Just as with the Cosmic Calendar of the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.87,0:38:10.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}未来年历上的每个月\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}every month the future calendar
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.17,0:38:12.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都相当于10亿年\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}equals about a billion years;
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.37,0:38:15.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每一天相当于4千万年\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}every day, some 40 million.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.51,0:38:19.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}科学使我们可以预测\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Science makes it possible for us to foretell
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.38,0:38:21.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}未来的某些天文事件\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}certain astronomical events
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.41,0:38:24.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使它发生在想象不到的遥远未来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in the unimaginably distant future--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.42,0:38:26.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}例如 太阳的死亡\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the death of the Sun, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.72,0:38:29.09,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在大约50亿年后\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In some five billion years,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.12,0:38:32.36,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这颗恒星会耗尽它的氢\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}our star will have exhausted its hydrogen--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.39,0:38:34.43,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是它的核能来源\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the nuclear fuel that powers it--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.46,0:38:36.59,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成为一颗红巨星\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}becoming a red giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.63,0:38:38.66,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这听起来很让人绝望\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I know that sounds depressing,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.70,0:38:41.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但如果人类能发挥出智慧\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but if we apply our intelligence, our descendants
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.60,0:38:44.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们在那遥远未来的后代\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of that distant future will have long departed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.70,0:38:47.51,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许早已远离了太阳系这个失落的世界\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from the lost worlds of the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.54,0:38:49.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天晓得\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.38,0:38:51.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类的活动带来了太多的变量\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Human events entail too many variables,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.41,0:38:53.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有太多的不确定性\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}too many uncertainties,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.15,0:38:55.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很难做出对人类未来的科学预测\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to make scientific statements about our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.71,0:38:57.78,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们依然梦想\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But we can still dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.82,0:39:00.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类的下一个黄金年代\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The next golden age of human achievement
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.59,0:39:02.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就开启于眼前此刻\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}begins here and now--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.79,0:39:06.72,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第二个宇宙年的元旦\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}New Year's Day of the next cosmic year.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.76,0:39:08.86,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在最初的十分之一秒内\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In the first tenth of a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.89,0:39:12.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人人都关爱蓝色的地球\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we take the vision of the pale blue dot to heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.16,0:39:15.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}学习与他人一同共享这个世界\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and learn how to share this tiny world with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.77,0:39:17.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后一台内燃机\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The last internal combustion engine
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.77,0:39:19.57,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被放进了博物馆\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is placed in a museum,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.61,0:39:22.37,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人对于气候的影响变小以至于消失\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as the effects of climate change reverse and diminish.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.41,0:39:26.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在未来的五分之一秒内\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A fifth of a second into this future
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.28,0:39:29.21,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类不再因贫穷而死去\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}people will stop dying from the effects of poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.25,0:39:32.28,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地球实现了完全的自给自足\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The planet is now a completely self-sustaining,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.32,0:39:34.72,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成为一个互通有无的大组织\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}intercommunicating organism.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.75,0:39:36.79,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}半秒过后\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A half-second from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.82,0:39:38.42,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}极地的冰帽开始\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the polar ice caps are restored
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.46,0:39:40.79,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恢复到19世纪的水平\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to the way they were in the 19th century,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.83,0:39:43.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}气候将会更加温和宜人\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the forecast is mild and pleasant
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.80,0:39:46.06,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在下一个1分半锺里\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for the next cosmic minute and a half--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.10,0:39:49.13,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是4万年\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}40,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.17,0:39:51.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到了人类已经开始\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By the time we are ready to settle
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.34,0:39:54.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}向最近的宜居星球殖民的时候\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even the nearest other planetary systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.04,0:39:56.84,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}世界已然大不同了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we will have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.88,0:39:59.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这简短的一段已然经过了许多代人\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The simple passage of so many generations
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.65,0:40:01.65,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类将会改变\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will have changed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.68,0:40:05.08,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自然规律会改变我们\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Necessity will have changed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.12,0:40:08.12,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们是善于适应环境的种族\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We are an adaptable species.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.86,0:40:12.26,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会是像我们这样的人抵达\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It will not be we who reach Alpha Centauri
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.29,0:40:14.36,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}半人马星座或者其它的恒星星系\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the other nearby star systems
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.39,0:40:16.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乘坐着星际方舟\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}on our interstellar arks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.50,0:40:19.10,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那应该是一个很像我们的物种\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It will be a species very like us,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.13,0:40:22.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比我们更强又没有我们的缺点\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but with more of our strengths and fewer of our weaknesses;
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.87,0:40:24.94,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更有自信 目光远大\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}more confident, far-seeing,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.97,0:40:27.67,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更有能力和智慧\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}capable and wise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.71,0:40:29.44,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然我们有种种弱点\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For all our failings,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.48,0:40:31.94,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}缺陷和局限性\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}despite our flaws and limitations,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.98,0:40:35.68,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们人类仍可称得上伟大\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we humans are capable of greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.71,0:40:38.95,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什么梦想在我们这个时代无法实现的话\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What new wonders, undreamt of in our time,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.98,0:40:42.49,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也会在下一代得以成真\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will we have accomplished in another generation...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.52,0:40:44.52,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或是再下下一代\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and another?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.76,0:40:47.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们这飘泊的种族\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How far will our nomadic species
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.93,0:40:51.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是否还要在下个世纪末\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}have wandered by the end of the next century,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.50,0:40:54.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或下一个千禧年时继续漫游？\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the next millennium?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.37,0:40:56.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们遥远的后代们\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our remote descendants,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.84,0:40:58.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许能安逸地活在其它的星球上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}safely arrayed on many worlds
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.74,0:41:01.34,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遍布整个太阳系甚至更遥远的地方\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}throughout the solar system and beyond,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.37,0:41:04.71,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们将会团结在共同的传统之下\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}will be unified by their common heritage,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.74,0:41:08.18,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}共同关注着他们的家园\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by their regard for their home planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.21,0:41:11.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}共同分享着知识\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and by their knowledge that, whatever other life may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.92,0:41:14.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管其它的生命是何种形式\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the only humans in all the universe
